ynthesis of the Shinto and Buddhist pantheons—prevalent during the Kamakura period.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 0aShin Buddhists. 4aAsian Studies : Asian Studies. 7aRELIGION / Eastern.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791480465423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791480465/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles